Title: Artisan's Supply: Chef's Smooth Rolling Pin
Description:
Are you looking for work, scribe?

I received an order from a company called the Artisan's Consortium.

It seems like a simple enough task for an apprentice crafter such as yourself.
ObjectivesText: Deliver a Chef's Smooth Rolling Pin to Haephesta at the Ruby Lifeshrine.

Objectives.Text: Deliver a Chef's Smooth Rolling Pin to Haephesta
